October 25, 2001

Notice #01-96


CORRECTION:


NOTICE OF  INTENTION TO TRANSFER MEMBERSHIP


             Please be advised that effective   with the open of business, October 25, 2001, the following member(s) have  given notice of intention to transfer their extra Membership within the  Exchange:


Eric Bolling  (RBI-4775)

Daniel Rappaport  (RAP-966)


             Members and Member Firms have (10) days from the date of this notice to  advise the Corporate Secretary's Office of any claims in accordance with Rule  2.51.


             Inquiries regarding the above should be addressed to the Member Services  Department at 212-299-2378.
